OL,5, Buy-now-pay-later firm Klarna will     
OL,6, start telling credit agencies who pays 
OL,7, on time and who falls behind.          
OL,9,FThe firm said the move could help or   
OL,10,Fhinder its customers' ability to get   
OL,11,Fcredit for loans such as mortgages.    
OL,13,FFrom June, banks and credit card firms 
OL,14,Fwill be able to see people's Klarna    
OL,15,Fhabits when making credit checks.      
OL,17,FCitizens Advice said buy-now-pay-later 
OL,18,F"can be like quicksand - easy to get   
OL,19,Finto but difficult to get out of" amid 
OL,20,Ffears it encourages people into debt.  
